{"tid":258096,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"奧雲講波以「We」形容曼聯　逾萬利迷聯署要求除名紅軍大使","createTime":"2017-05-25T19:09:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-26T01:57:02.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"127c7a35eef2cbb8167c3d5a4311fe2f03d27cd1","tid":258096,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T19:09:20.000Z","msg":"曼聯今晨以2：0擊敗阿積士奪得歐霸盃，事件引起另一場風波。事關英國《BT Sport》直播這場賽事時，找來「曼聯名宿」兼前利物浦球星奧雲擔任評述，由於當提及曼聯時他都以「We（我們）」來形容，激發紅軍球迷發起網上聯署，要求利物浦官方將奧雲的球會國際足球大使職銜除名。發起聯署不足一天，已經有超過1萬名球迷參與。<br />\n<br />\n網上聯署上表示，身為利物浦球會國際足球大使的奧雲，不但未有百份百支持紅軍，還以「我們」去形容死敵曼聯，等同公開支持對手，對利物浦零尊重。聯署又形容繼續由奧雲出任球會國際足球大使是「恥辱」，故發起網上聯署要求對方「除名」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.telegraph.co.uk/multimedia/archive/01910/michael-owen_1910005c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.telegraph.co.uk%2Fmultimedia%2Farchive%2F01910%2Fmichael-owen_1910005c.jpg&h=bd717133&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8e090252fa447aadd694d26e5dff1ec0d90b0e8","tid":258096,"uid":1453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T19:11:45.000Z","msg":"咁人地曼聯名宿黎"},{"pid":"38e879cdfa355af92545a77879d6d78d2ffaed08","tid":258096,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T19:14:02.000Z","msg":"利狗=小氣鬼"},{"pid":"df670a8302ea5141116d2fd8895ed1c5135ba2a5","tid":258096,"uid":760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-25T19:22:06.000Z","msg":"怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ba93e0c4eca8fa7588d6795fe532c2dce64209","tid":258096,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T00:39:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0d3b1586c050969c4e7646b7933ff93977b90dc6","tid":258096,"uid":759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T00:53:38.000Z","msg":"奧雲仔真係曼聯歷史以來最佳收購<br />\n激到垃圾猁紮紮跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg